{"tid":2063553,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP到大陸當演員了","createTime":"2020-06-14T06:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:03:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c36587dd8a23cf58f8c1be9d5b9665c45e6aac88","tid":2063553,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"一手創立JYP娛樂的朴軫永（JYP）是南韓三大經紀公司創辦人中，唯一持續推出作品活躍在舞台上的一位，不過最近卻有大陸網友截圖討論：「JYP來中國當演員了？」結果點開照片一看，網友笑到狂刷一排「哈哈哈哈哈哈」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4938/d4938968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4938%2Fd4938968.jpg&h=cbf691df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲在《陳芊芊》中飾演「孟過」的沈馳（圖右）撞臉JYP。（圖／翻攝自朴軫永IG、微博）<br />\n<br />\n網友截圖的演員本尊其實是一名大陸男演員沈馳，在夯劇《傳聞中的陳芊芊》飾演威猛山的山匪首領「孟過」，後來歸順陳芊芊，自願退居為二當家。日前《陳芊芊》劇組舉辦慶功粉絲見面會，他卸掉劇中的大鬍子清爽現身，結果一張側臉照被誤以為是JYP。<br />\n<br />\n有網友笑著說沈馳像是清秀版的JYP，也有人震驚地問：「所以...難道他不是JYP嗎」、「真的不是嗎？這也太像了吧！」還有網友以JYP的口吻幽默笑稱：「攤牌了，其實我是演員。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4938/4938970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4938%2F4938970.jpg&h=94d99905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友評論刷一堆「哈哈哈」。（圖／翻攝自朴軫永IG、微博）<br />\n<br />\n事實上JYP的長相辨識度非常高，日前在推特上有張照片廣為流傳，照片裡是兩個小朋友，灰色上衣的小朋友站立在欄杆前，一手搭在身旁小朋友的腰上保護著，另一個穿著牛仔吊帶褲、年紀比較小的小朋友則是坐在欄杆上。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/maneuI/status/1260524356146311168?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1260524356146311168&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1737532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FmaneuI%2Fstatus%2F1260524356146311168%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1260524356146311168%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1737532&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=dda2ed0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FmaneuI%2Fstatus%2F1260524356146311168%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1260524356146311168%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1737532&h=5c520a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/maneuI/status/1260524356146311168?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1260524356146311168&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1737532</a><br />\nPO照片的網友說：「我完全不需要說他是誰，你們看就知道了。」果然網友立刻刷一排正確答案：「朴軫永！」比對童年時期和現在的模樣，朴軫永的五官幾乎沒什麼不同，大概只有縮小跟放大的差別。"},{"pid":"adf376ceb0046322d5093327ace0d3ce57559ef6","tid":2063553,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"又真係有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}